title: Live From The Minneapolis Comedy Festival W DC Young Fly Karlous Miller  Chico Bean | Ep. 190
itunes:title: Live From The Minneapolis Comedy Festival W DC Young Fly Karlous Miller  Chico Bean | Ep. 190
description:
The next generation of comedy superstars take that stage at The State Theater to cap off The Minneapolis Comedy Festival. DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean take a trip down memory lane, twerk with the fans and roast everybody. The 85 South Show brought the hood out and turnt up! Minnesota definitely piped up and showed what they all about!
